question: Andrea is required to submit a 212-page dissertation. She already finished writing 1/2 of the dissertation. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Andrea has already written 1/2 of the dissertation which is 212 pages*1/2 = <<212*1/2=106>>106 pages.
So, she still needs to write 212 pages - 106 pages = <<212-106=106>>106 pages.
#### 106
